milestones.description: Malla and Rohit Paudel's 89-run partnership is NEP's highest for the 3rd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 62 between Vesawkar and Airee
Karan KC and Rohit Paudel's 65-run partnership is NEP's highest for the 7th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 40 between Sompal Kami and Aarif Sheikh
Norman Vanua has broken the record for most sixes (20) in ODIs for PNG, going past Tony Ura's 19
Karan KC has broken the record for most sixes in an innings (4) in ODIs for NEP, going past Sompal Kami's 3
Lamichhane has taken the most five-wicket hauls (2) in ODIs for NEP, going past Sompal Kami's record
This is the highest match aggregate (315) involving teams P.N.G. & Nepal in ODIs
Nepal's 151-run win against P.N.G. is the largest margin of victory in terms of runs in ODIs, beating 145-run win against U.A.E.
Lamichhane has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (12) for NEP, going past Aarif Sheikh
Malla and Rohit Paudel's 89-run partnership is NEP's highest for any wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 84 between Kushal Malla and Bhandari
